{"tid":726300,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"在屍體旁進食","createTime":"2018-07-02T09:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T03:44:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"074a5749cd99222c765d20d3972aed5f7ebb856d","tid":726300,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180702/20437245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F20437245&d=wJQDztqai%2BickeFlznggjUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f0da2b66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F20437245&h=3d44ced6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180702/20437245</a><br />\n<br />\n在屍體旁進食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180702/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180702%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=c1f9c147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網絡視頻截圖<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n中國某地一群同學搞「老同學聚會」，包起一間山莊吃喝。其間有女同學上台致辭時懷疑心臟病發作，當場倒地不起。她的老同學們圍上去，有人探她鼻息，有人摸她脈搏，雖然現場並無醫生，但這些人憑經驗斷定倒地者已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n中國人是現實的，既然「死都死了」，活着的人還要繼續活下去的，點了的酒菜也不能浪費，所以他們像甚麼事也沒發生過一樣，任由屍體躺在腳下，繼續吃吃喝喝、談笑風生。有個男同學甚至在網絡直播，笑着說他們的同學聚會上有人死了，「真夠嗆的，可能心臟有事吧。」不知道他在笑甚麼？大約覺得可以直播老同學死亡很有趣。<br />\n<br />\n若83年高中畢業時是18歲，那這群人生於1965年，今天都已年過半百，但尚未退休，是上有老下有小的夾心階層。如果說他們的價值觀承上啟下，上來自父母，下傳承子女，那麼，就很恐怖了。<br />\n<br />\n一個活人在眼皮底下出事，約出來聚會的老同學居然無人出手相救，連打電話報警的人都沒有。冷血程度令人髮指。不知那女人臨死前在台上致辭時說了甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n如果說的是「幾十年友情從未褪色」，那就真正諷刺了。有人說，在中國出手救人做心外壓，萬一結果仍是回天乏術，就有機會被死者家屬告。這個隱憂也許符合中國國情，但觀乎那一群人，有嘻嘻笑笑拍片的，有若無其事繼續進食的，有事不關己地說「死都死了」的，看不出他們曾在救與不救間掙扎。地下躺着個死人，旁邊全是活死人。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=wJQDztqai%2BickeFlznggjUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f16298fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n三十歲後不聽新歌？ (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n不曾逢着獨醒人 (古德明)"},{"pid":"b328d2612629fb3ef6a67b992a9cd11db5b9447e","tid":726300,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ba6dfc844f99f31deaeb0759baca9cc9e50464","tid":726300,"uid":192697,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"f0a46e242e84aa09b48299c638733226622d8ca0","tid":726300,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"冇人急救On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40e76b7e25df0953bb13f5d46847941a0a66ce6","tid":726300,"uid":66527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"遲d到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32870de0c4a6e15ec87e715fd7aeb9a271a0aa04","tid":726300,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0a46e242e84aa09b48299c638733226622d8ca0","tid":726300,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"冇人急救On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"閒事莫理"},{"pid":"7652b98a5cd1d500b5b427fa0f029136f7ee23a1","tid":726300,"uid":66825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"人情冷暖"},{"pid